            ' data-v-80333db8> <p data-v-80333db8>\n      Hi! I\'m Mariko, a city enthusiast currently traveling around the world.\n      I\'m a researcher, editor and writer on the urban issues, and I have been involved in the various international urban programs and initiatives all over the world.\n    </p> <p data-v-80333db8><strong data-v-80333db8>\n        As an Urbanist,\n      </strong>\n      I\'m most passionate about our cities. I’ve involved in many international educational projects like <a href="http://www.4cities.eu/" target="_blank" data-v-80333db8>4CITIES</a>, <a href="https://www.urbandivercities.eu/" target="_blank" data-v-80333db8>DIVERCITIES</a>, and have visited more than 120 organizations and 50 cities accross the globe for research. More specifically I’m interested in ethno-cultural diversity in our cities, and the notion of nationality and sense of belonging.\n    </p> <p data-v-80333db8><strong data-v-80333db8>\n        As a project manager,\n      </strong>\n      Having worked in a design firm <a href="https://loftwork.com/en/" target="_blank" data-v-80333db8>Loftwork</a> as a director and marketer, I organize various events and workshops in collaboration with the international organizations, such as 2 days workshop <a href="https://medium.com/digitalsocietyschool/global-goals-jam-2017-tokyo-6141f938b7d3" target="_blank" data-v-80333db8>Global Goals Jam</a> and <a href="https://loftwork.com/jp/event/20170829_sgs_report" target="_blank" data-v-80333db8>Social Good Summit Tokyo</a>, or more urbanism related events like <a href="https://medium.com/@mariko9012/subjective-map-workshop-shibuya-712e92d21051" target="_blank" data-v-80333db8>subjective map workshop</a> and <a href="https://medium.com/@mariko9012/urbanist-meetup-tokyo-examining-the-role-of-urbanists-in-improving-urban-life-in-tokyo-df2e5bdea51a" target="_blank" data-v-80333db8>urbanist meetup</a>.\n    </p> <p data-v-80333db8><strong data-v-80333db8>\n        As a writer / translator,\n      </strong>\n        I work across the spectrum of urban design, urbanism and architecture. For the past 6 years, I’ve conducted various in depth field research/interviews across the world and have written the analytical articles and papers as a freelance writer.\n    </p> <p data-v-80333db8><strong data-v-80333db8>\n        Personally,\n      </strong>\n      I\'m a huge traveler – I’ve lived in ten different cities, in seven different countries. I’m always passionate about making my homes everywhere in the world!\n    </p> <p data-v-80333db8>\n      If you\'re interested in working together, or just to have a cup of coffee to know what I’m up to, please <a href="mailto:mariko9012@gmail.com" data-v-80333db8>email me</a> or check out my <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mariko-sugita-28327bb6/" target="_blank" data-v-80333db8>LinkedIn page</a>!\n    </p> <p class="sub" data-v-80333db8><i data-v-80333db8>Special thanks to <a href="http://www.jasperstephenson.com" target="_blank" data-v-80333db8>Jasper Stephenson</a> for mentorship and coding help on this site!</i></p>') +
